</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[1436,2537,1358,1391]" pageId="9" pageNumber="202" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="9.[1436,2642,968,1746]" box="[1436,2537,1358,1391]" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1436,1671,1358,1391]" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Van Zyl’s Golden Mole is expected to be primarily nocturnal.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[1438,2376,1401,1430]" pageId="9" pageNumber="202" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph blockId="9.[1436,2642,968,1746]" box="[1438,2376,1401,1430]" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1438,2137,1401,1430]" pageId="9" pageNumber="202">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
